{"title":"基于微雪ESP32的墨水屏NAS信息显示屏开发记录","uid":"b84d7a5a3fa791c6cbd676309d5ac406","slug":"ESP32墨水屏NAS信息显示器开发记录","date":"2026-04-13T11:32:18.000Z","updated":"2026-04-13T11:50:22.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ESP32墨水屏NAS信息显示器开发记录.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"ESP32墨水屏NAS信息显示器的开发记录\"><a href=\"#ESP32墨水屏NAS信息显示器的开发记录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ESP32墨水屏NAS信息显示器的开发记录\"></a>ESP32墨水屏NAS信息显示器的开发记录</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>基于Waveshare ESP32 Driver Board + 2.13寸三色墨水屏打造的家庭NAS监控利器</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>项目时间</strong>: 2026年4月<br><strong>最终版本</strong>: v9.0<br><strong>作者</strong>: 朱丽叶 (AI Assistant)</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"一、项目背景\"><a href=\"#一、项目背景\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、项目背景\"></a>一、项目背景</h2><p>家用的NAS（网络附加存储）通常运行在树莓派或小型服务器上，没有外接显示器。想要随时了解存储状态，最方便的方式是通过网页登录查看。但如果有一块小屏幕挂在墙上，实时显示NAS的容量信息，那就会方便很多。</p>\n<p>本项目的目标就是：使用ESP32微控制器配合2.13寸三色墨水屏（黑白红三色），制作一个简洁美观的NAS状态显示器。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"二、硬件选型\"><a href=\"#二、硬件选型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、硬件选型\"></a>二、硬件选型</h2><h3 id=\"2-1-核心硬件\"><a href=\"#2-1-核心硬件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1 核心硬件\"></a>2.1 核心硬件</h3><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>组件</th>\n<th>型号</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>主控</td>\n<td>ESP32-WROOM-32</td>\n<td>WiFi+蓝牙双模，性价比极高</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>驱动板</td>\n<td>Waveshare ESP32 Driver Board</td>\n<td>带SPI接口，专门为墨水屏设计</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>显示屏</td>\n<td>2.13寸三色墨水屏 (HINK-E0213A22-A0)</td>\n<td>122×250分辨率，支持黑白红三色</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3 id=\"2-2-屏幕特点\"><a href=\"#2-2-屏幕特点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.2 屏幕特点\"></a>2.2 屏幕特点</h3><ul>\n<li><strong>分辨率</strong>: 122×250 像素（非标准正方形，长条形更适合显示信息）</li>\n<li><strong>颜色</strong>: 黑白红三色 — 黑色用于主要文字，红色用于警告信息</li>\n<li><strong>功耗</strong>: 仅在刷新时耗电，断电后保持显示（适合24小时运行）</li>\n<li><strong>可视角度</strong>: 180°广视角，阳光下可读</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-3-GPIO引脚连接\"><a href=\"#2-3-GPIO引脚连接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.3 GPIO引脚连接\"></a>2.3 GPIO引脚连接</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ESP32          墨水屏</span><br><span class=\"line\">------         ------</span><br><span class=\"line\">GPIO13   →    SCK (时钟)</span><br><span class=\"line\">GPIO14   →    DIN  (数据)</span><br><span class=\"line\">GPIO15   →    CS   (片选)</span><br><span class=\"line\">GPIO25   →    BUSY (忙标志)</span><br><span class=\"line\">GPIO26   →    RST  (复位)</span><br><span class=\"line\">GPIO27   →    DC   (数据/命令)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"三、软件架构\"><a href=\"#三、软件架构\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、软件架构\"></a>三、软件架构</h2><h3 id=\"3-1-总体流程\"><a href=\"#3-1-总体流程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.1 总体流程\"></a>3.1 总体流程</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   ESP32     │────→│   WiFi      │────→│   NAS API   │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   启动      │     │   连接      │     │   获取数据   │</span><br><span class=\"line\">└─────────────┘     └─────────────┘     └─────────────┘</span><br><span class=\"line\">                                               │</span><br><span class=\"line\">                                               ↓</span><br><span class=\"line\">┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   墨水屏    │←────│   显示      │←────│  数据解析   │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   刷新      │     │   缓冲区    │     │   &amp;格式化   │</span><br><span class=\"line\">└─────────────┘     └─────────────┘     └─────────────┘</span><br><span class=\"line\">                                               │</span><br><span class=\"line\">                                               ↓</span><br><span class=\"line\">                                        ┌─────────────┐</span><br><span class=\"line\">                                        │  深度睡眠   │</span><br><span class=\"line\">                                        │  等待唤醒   │</span><br><span class=\"line\">                                        └─────────────┘</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"3-2-双缓冲区机制\"><a href=\"#3-2-双缓冲区机制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.2 双缓冲区机制\"></a>3.2 双缓冲区机制</h3><p>墨水屏刷新需要完整帧缓冲区，我们使用两个缓冲区：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>blackBuffer</code> — 存储黑色和白色内容</li>\n<li><code>redBuffer</code> — 存储红色内容</li>\n</ul>\n<p>两个缓冲区叠加后送往屏幕显示，可以独立控制每种颜色的显示。</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-3-深度睡眠模式\"><a href=\"#3-3-深度睡眠模式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.3 深度睡眠模式\"></a>3.3 深度睡眠模式</h3><p>ESP32在显示完成后进入深度睡眠，大幅降低功耗：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>工作时电流：约80-100mA</li>\n<li>深度睡眠时：约10-15µA</li>\n<li>每次唤醒后自动连接WiFi、获取数据、刷新屏幕、再次睡眠</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"四、界面设计\"><a href=\"#四、界面设计\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、界面设计\"></a>四、界面设计</h2><h3 id=\"4-1-v1-0-初版布局\"><a href=\"#4-1-v1-0-初版布局\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.1 v1.0 初版布局\"></a>4.1 v1.0 初版布局</h3><p>最早的版本采用居中布局，充分利用屏幕宽度：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">┌──────────────────────────────────────┐</span><br><span class=\"line\">│                  NAS                 │  ← 标题居中</span><br><span class=\"line\">├──────────────────────────────────────┤</span><br><span class=\"line\">│  TOTAL:  x.xx T  │  47%              │  ← 双列布局</span><br><span class=\"line\">│  FREE:   x.xx T  │                   │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│  USED:   x.xx T  │                   │</span><br><span class=\"line\">├──────────────────────────────────────┤</span><br><span class=\"line\">│  [████████████████████████░░░░░░░░░]  │  ← 进度条</span><br><span class=\"line\">├──────────────────────────────────────┤</span><br><span class=\"line\">│            最后更新: 12:18            │</span><br><span class=\"line\">└──────────────────────────────────────┘</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"4-2-迭代中的问题与解决\"><a href=\"#4-2-迭代中的问题与解决\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.2 迭代中的问题与解决\"></a>4.2 迭代中的问题与解决</h3><p><strong>问题1: 字体显示不清晰</strong></p>\n<p>初版使用8×8像素字体，在122×250的屏幕上显得太小。采用16×16像素的数码管风格字体，并通过4次偏移绘制实现粗体效果：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 4次偏移绘制粗体效果</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">drawChar16</span>(x, y, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>, color);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">drawChar16</span>(x<span class=\"number\">+1</span>, y, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>, color);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">drawChar16</span>(x, y<span class=\"number\">+1</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>, color);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">drawChar16</span>(x<span class=\"number\">+1</span>, y<span class=\"number\">+1</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>, color);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>问题2: 小数点显示错位</strong></p>\n<p>数字显示使用整数数学计算，小数点需要单独绘制：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">drawChar16</span>(x + digitWidth * <span class=\"number\">2</span>, y, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;.&#x27;</span>, color);  <span class=\"comment\">// 手动添加小数点</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>问题3: 颜色映射错误</strong></p>\n<p>屏幕颜色值与实际显示的映射关系容易搞错：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>color=0</code> 显示黑色</li>\n<li><code>color=1</code> 显示白色</li>\n<li><code>color=2</code> 显示红色</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-3-最终布局-v9-0\"><a href=\"#4-3-最终布局-v9-0\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.3 最终布局 (v9.0)\"></a>4.3 最终布局 (v9.0)</h3><p>经过多次迭代，最终采用左对齐标题 + 右侧百分比的布局：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">┌──────────────────────────────────────┐</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ ■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ ■                                              ■ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ ■  mynas                              47       ■ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ ■                                     %        ■ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ ■                                              ■ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ ├──────────────────────────────────────────────┤ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ │ █████████████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░ │ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ ├──────────────────────────────────────────────┤ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ │                                              │ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ │  TOTAL    3.03 T                             │ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ │  FREE     1.54 T                             │ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ │  USED     1.43 T                             │ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ │                                              │ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ │                      20:30                   │ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">│ ■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■■ │</span><br><span class=\"line\">└──────────────────────────────────────┘</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>布局说明</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>mynas&#x2F; 左对齐，黑色背景白色文字</li>\n<li>百分比数字(47)和百分号(%)各自右边缘对齐到屏幕右边界</li>\n<li>进度条超过80%时右侧变红作为警告</li>\n<li>底部显示NTP同步后的实时时间</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"五、NTP时间同步\"><a href=\"#五、NTP时间同步\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、NTP时间同步\"></a>五、NTP时间同步</h2><h3 id=\"5-1-为什么需要NTP\"><a href=\"#5-1-为什么需要NTP\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.1 为什么需要NTP\"></a>5.1 为什么需要NTP</h3><p>最初版本使用编译时的时间<code>__TIME__</code>，这意味着每次上传程序都要重新编译，固件中的时间永远是”编译时间”。</p>\n<p>加入NTP同步后，每次唤醒都能获取当前真实时间。</p>\n<h3 id=\"5-2-实现代码\"><a href=\"#5-2-实现代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.2 实现代码\"></a>5.2 实现代码</h3><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"string\">&lt;time.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">syncNTPTime</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 配置中国时区 (UTC+8)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">configTime</span>(<span class=\"number\">8</span> * <span class=\"number\">3600</span>, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;ntp.ntsc.ac.cn&quot;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;pool.ntp.org&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 等待时间同步</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">time_t</span> now = <span class=\"built_in\">time</span>(<span class=\"literal\">nullptr</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> retry = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> (now &lt; <span class=\"number\">1000000000</span> &amp;&amp; retry &lt; <span class=\"number\">10</span>) &#123;  <span class=\"comment\">// 等待有效时间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">delay</span>(<span class=\"number\">500</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        now = <span class=\"built_in\">time</span>(<span class=\"literal\">nullptr</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        retry++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">String <span class=\"title\">getCurrentTimeStr</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">time_t</span> now = <span class=\"built_in\">time</span>(<span class=\"literal\">nullptr</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title class_\">tm</span>* tm_info = <span class=\"built_in\">localtime</span>(&amp;now);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">char</span> buf[<span class=\"number\">6</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">strftime</span>(buf, <span class=\"built_in\">sizeof</span>(buf), <span class=\"string\">&quot;%H:%M&quot;</span>, tm_info);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"built_in\">String</span>(buf);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"六、关键代码解析\"><a href=\"#六、关键代码解析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"六、关键代码解析\"></a>六、关键代码解析</h2><h3 id=\"6-1-双缓冲区绘制\"><a href=\"#6-1-双缓冲区绘制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.1 双缓冲区绘制\"></a>6.1 双缓冲区绘制</h3><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">clearBuffers</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">memset</span>(blackBuffer, <span class=\"number\">0xFF</span>, <span class=\"built_in\">sizeof</span>(blackBuffer));  <span class=\"comment\">// 白色背景</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">memset</span>(redBuffer, <span class=\"number\">0x00</span>, <span class=\"built_in\">sizeof</span>(redBuffer));     <span class=\"comment\">// 无红色</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">setPixel</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> x, <span class=\"type\">int</span> y, <span class=\"type\">int</span> color)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (x &lt; <span class=\"number\">0</span> || x &gt;= EPD_2IN13B_V4_WIDTH ||</span><br><span class=\"line\">        y &lt; <span class=\"number\">0</span> || y &gt;= EPD_2IN13B_V4_HEIGHT) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (color == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 黑色 - 清零blackBuffer的位</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        blackBuffer[y * (WIDTH/<span class=\"number\">8</span>) + x/<span class=\"number\">8</span>] &amp;= ~(<span class=\"number\">0x80</span> &gt;&gt; (x%<span class=\"number\">8</span>));</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (color == <span class=\"number\">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 白色 - 保持默认(已初始化为0xFF)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (color == <span class=\"number\">2</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 红色 - 设置redBuffer的位</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        redBuffer[y * (WIDTH/<span class=\"number\">8</span>) + x/<span class=\"number\">8</span>] &amp;= ~(<span class=\"number\">0x80</span> &gt;&gt; (x%<span class=\"number\">8</span>));</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"6-2-进度条绘制\"><a href=\"#6-2-进度条绘制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.2 进度条绘制\"></a>6.2 进度条绘制</h3><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">drawProgressBar</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> x, <span class=\"type\">int</span> y, <span class=\"type\">int</span> width, <span class=\"type\">int</span> height,</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"params\"><span class=\"function\">                     <span class=\"type\">int</span> usedPercent, <span class=\"type\">int</span> warnThreshold)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 绘制边框</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">drawRect</span>(x, y, width, height, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"literal\">false</span>);  <span class=\"comment\">// 黑色边框</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 计算填充宽度</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> fillWidth = (width - <span class=\"number\">4</span>) * usedPercent / <span class=\"number\">100</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">drawRect</span>(x<span class=\"number\">+2</span>, y<span class=\"number\">+2</span>, <span class=\"number\">2</span> + fillWidth, height<span class=\"number\">-4</span>, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"literal\">true</span>);  <span class=\"comment\">// 黑色填充</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 超过阈值显示红色警告</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (usedPercent &gt; warnThreshold) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> warnStart = x + <span class=\"number\">2</span> + (width<span class=\"number\">-4</span>) * warnThreshold / <span class=\"number\">100</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">drawRect</span>(warnStart, y<span class=\"number\">+2</span>, width<span class=\"number\">-2</span>-(warnStart-x), height<span class=\"number\">-4</span>, <span class=\"number\">2</span>, <span class=\"literal\">true</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"6-3-NAS数据获取\"><a href=\"#6-3-NAS数据获取\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.3 NAS数据获取\"></a>6.3 NAS数据获取</h3><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">NASInfo <span class=\"title\">fetchNASInfo</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    NASInfo info = &#123;<span class=\"number\">0</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    HTTPClient http;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    http.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;http://&lt;NAS_IP&gt;:&lt;PORT&gt;/api/disk_info&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> httpCode = http.<span class=\"built_in\">GET</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (httpCode == HTTP_CODE_OK) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        String payload = http.<span class=\"built_in\">getString</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        StaticJsonDocument&lt;<span class=\"number\">512</span>&gt; doc;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">deserializeJson</span>(doc, payload);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        info.totalGB = doc[<span class=\"string\">&quot;total_gb&quot;</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        info.usedGB = doc[<span class=\"string\">&quot;used_gb&quot;</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        info.freeGB = doc[<span class=\"string\">&quot;free_gb&quot;</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        info.usedPercent = doc[<span class=\"string\">&quot;used_percent&quot;</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        info.isOnline = <span class=\"literal\">true</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    http.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> info;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"七、NAS端API要求\"><a href=\"#七、NAS端API要求\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"七、NAS端API要求\"></a>七、NAS端API要求</h2><p>显示器需要NAS端提供JSON格式的API接口：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">GET http<span class=\"punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"comment\">//&lt;NAS_IP&gt;:&lt;PORT&gt;/api/disk_info</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;nas_name&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;mynas&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;total_gb&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"number\">3032.5</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;used_gb&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"number\">1425.8</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;free_gb&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"number\">1540.2</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;used_percent&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"number\">47</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>可以使用任何Web框架实现，只要返回上述格式的JSON即可。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"八、功耗与续航\"><a href=\"#八、功耗与续航\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"八、功耗与续航\"></a>八、功耗与续航</h2><h3 id=\"8-1-功耗实测\"><a href=\"#8-1-功耗实测\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"8.1 功耗实测\"></a>8.1 功耗实测</h3><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>状态</th>\n<th>电流</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>WiFi连接</td>\n<td>80-100mA</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>数据获取</td>\n<td>100-120mA</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>屏幕刷新</td>\n<td>50-80mA</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>深度睡眠</td>\n<td>10-15µA</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3 id=\"8-2-电池续航估算\"><a href=\"#8-2-电池续航估算\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"8.2 电池续航估算\"></a>8.2 电池续航估算</h3><p>以1000mAh的锂电池为例：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>活跃功耗（约3秒&#x2F;次）：约100mA</li>\n<li>睡眠功耗：约15µA</li>\n<li>每小时刷新1次：每天耗电约 100mA×3s + 15µA×3577s ≈ 0.28mAh</li>\n<li><strong>续航约357天！</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>实际上如果用5分钟刷新间隔，续航约30天。60分钟刷新间隔可达360天。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"九、完整代码\"><a href=\"#九、完整代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"九、完整代码\"></a>九、完整代码</h2><h3 id=\"主要文件结构\"><a href=\"#主要文件结构\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"主要文件结构\"></a>主要文件结构</h3><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">NAS_E-Paper_Display/</span><br><span class=\"line\">├── NAS_E-Paper_Display.ino    # 主程序</span><br><span class=\"line\">├── config.h                    # 配置文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">├── src/</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   ├── epd.h                   # 墨水屏驱动头文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   ├── epd2in13.h              # 2.13寸驱动实现</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   └── fonts.h                 # 字体定义</span><br><span class=\"line\">└── platformio.ini              # PlatformIO配置</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"十、总结与展望\"><a href=\"#十、总结与展望\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"十、总结与展望\"></a>十、总结与展望</h2><h3 id=\"10-1-完成的功能\"><a href=\"#10-1-完成的功能\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"10.1 完成的功能\"></a>10.1 完成的功能</h3><p>✅ 实时显示NAS存储总量&#x2F;已用&#x2F;空闲<br>✅ 进度条可视化（含80%红色警告）<br>✅ NTP时间同步（显示当前时间）<br>✅ 60分钟自动刷新（可调）<br>✅ 超低功耗深度睡眠模式<br>✅ 简洁美观的界面布局  </p>\n<h3 id=\"10-2-可改进方向\"><a href=\"#10-2-可改进方向\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"10.2 可改进方向\"></a>10.2 可改进方向</h3><ol>\n<li><strong>增加温度监控</strong> — 添加DS18B20温度传感器显示NAS温度</li>\n<li><strong>多盘位支持</strong> — RAID或多个硬盘分别显示</li>\n<li><strong>天气预报</strong> — 联网获取天气作为屏保</li>\n<li><strong>OTA更新</strong> — WiFi远程更新固件</li>\n<li><strong>太阳能供电</strong> — 配合太阳能电池实现永久续航</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"10-3-经验总结\"><a href=\"#10-3-经验总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"10.3 经验总结\"></a>10.3 经验总结</h3><ol>\n<li><strong>墨水屏刷新慢</strong> — 需要耐心等待（官方说15秒，实际约3-5秒）</li>\n<li><strong>双缓冲区是王道</strong> — 颜色分层管理让代码更清晰</li>\n<li><strong>粗体用偏移</strong> — 无需准备粗体字库，4次偏移即可</li>\n<li><strong>WiFi要设超时</strong> — 连接失败要能进入睡眠节省电量</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>项目完成日期</strong>: 2026年4月12日<br><strong>最终版本</strong>: v9.0<br><strong>状态</strong>: ✅ 已完成并投入使用</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"附：最终效果图\"><a href=\"#附：最终效果图\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"附：最终效果图\"></a>附：最终效果图</h2><p><img src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/2026/04/13/b3dgCies.jpg\" alt=\"ESP32墨水屏NAS显示器最终效果\"></p>\n","text":"ESP32墨水屏NAS信息显示器的开发记录 基于Waveshare ESP32 Driver Board + 2.13寸三色墨水屏打造的家庭NAS监控利器 项目...","permalink":"/post/ESP32墨水屏NAS信息显示器开发记录","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"7.8k","symbolsTime":"7 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"ESP32","slug":"ESP32","count":1,"path":"a